{"tid":1506933,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"用曱甴去形容市民 目的就系要屠殺","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:59:49.000Z","uid":274761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da19d26779420327355b11a6826748e3063e1d51","tid":1506933,"uid":274761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"1994年(25年前)的<span style=\"color: red;\">盧旺達大屠殺</span>中高達<span style=\"color: red;\">100萬人被殺</span>，發生屠殺之前，<span style=\"color: red;\">胡圖族用「曱甴」等詞語形容圖西族</span>。結果當屠殺黎到的時候，殺人者佢地只系殺死左好多「曱甴」，而唔系殺人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n別小看這些「非人化」形容詞，言語暴力只系第一步，終章就系要藍絲可以對黃絲／示威者進行冷血的謀殺！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">景林連儂牆系好例子</span></span></strong>，藍絲對幾個手無串鐵進行謀殺（一個女生危殆）。一個正常人，唔系兩軍對壘的時候，點可能落手咁重？因為佢唔當黃絲系人，只系「曱甴」，而且佢知道咁樣落手都無咩後果！<br />\n<br />\n我跪求大家，千祈唔可以俾ＥＤ咁的形容詞繼續發酵落去，唔系的話Ｄ手足只會愈黎愈傷，甚至令到Ｄ藍絲變成屠殺機器！<br />\n<br />\n另外希望推上國際，俾Ｄ外國人（唔計法國）知道，中共／香港做緊Ｄ咩的仆街野！警察同屈穎妍意識展開屠殺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n探討何謂非人化及論其對社會的危險性<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%8E%E4%BD%95%E8%AC%82%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8A%E8%AB%96%E5%85%B6%E5%B0%8D%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E6%80%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25A8%258E%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25AC%2582%25E9%259D%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E6%2580%25A7%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=045d7c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25A8%258E%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25AC%2582%25E9%259D%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E6%2580%25A7%2F&h=2113216f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%8E%E4%BD%95%E8%AC%82%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8A%E8%AB%96%E5%85%B6%E5%B0%8D%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E6%80%A7/</a><br />\n<br />\n盧安達大屠殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%A2%E6%97%BA%E8%BE%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258D%25A2%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25BE%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%259D%2580%23%25E8%2583%258C%25E6%2599%25AF&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=5e77c527\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%A2%E6%97%BA%E8%BE%BE%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n警察及屈穎妍用「曱甴」形容示烕者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/364358/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%90%E6%9C%83%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8-%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E4%B8%8D%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8D%E7%A6%AE%E8%B2%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F364358%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2583%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E8%25B2%258C&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=52100b31\" target=\"_bla