/>\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8deedce1621dde590d9e046aa001d6e244f4979","tid":1506933,"uid":274761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"自推. 認真推, 警察內裏可能就系有咁的思想, 先愈打愈毒"}]}